{"name":"Link Between Worlds","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Link Between Worlds</p>\n<p>When you open a portal between this world and your tethered realm, roll+INT.</p>\n<p>On a 10+ the portal is open long enough for a group of creatures to make it through.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9 the portal is unstable, and could close at any time.</p>","class":"The Summoner","rollType":"INT","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"lLvk0DQuIPGL48Iv"}
